reviewText:
There are only five episodes on this DVD that are on the main volumes.
The episodes on this volume are:
1. Family Picture (also found on All You Need Is Love and Pasta)
2. Virtual Odeon (also found on Spooky Tails)
3. Mastermind (also found on Spooky Tails)
4. History of Dogs (also found on Dinosaurs & Other Animal Adventures)
5. From The Oven (also found on Odie Oh!)
There are no Garfield shorts on this disk.
